{"tid":2442710,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[港台]日常8點半 星期一至五 2030-2130（2)","createTime":"2021-03-11T13:49:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-24T12:53:52.000Z","uid":30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"38b935e62b6cfc6b1c572327570b0655421c6119","tid":2442710,"uid":30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T13:49:50.000Z","msg":"一個集合旅遊、飲食、健康、消閒、電影以及民生等熱門話題的雜誌式節目，逢星期一至五晚上八點半，主持人陳逸寧（Isabel）、譚淇淇（淇淇）、潘杰寧（Kelena）、李蔓瑩（Renee）、陳倩揚、鄭萃雯、伍家謙（家謙）、黎國輝（阿感）、泰山、林子博，司勳，與城中各界嘉賓無所不談，一於日日有主題，晚晚有話題。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/assets/rthk/images/programme/dtt31/830mag_4/8154_programme_slider_29636_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Fassets%2Frthk%2Fimages%2Fprogramme%2Fdtt31%2F830mag_4%2F8154_programme_slider_29636_0.jpg&h=05bfed00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n此外，一群活力充沛的「830特工隊」還會四出搜羅貼地的城市熱話，追蹤社會所見所聞。輕輕鬆鬆，資訊爆發一個鐘！"},{"pid":"1d94367d9ad628d8e55b4212f0df24cddec24601","tid":2442710,"uid":278551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T14:08:03.000Z","msg":"陳逸寧、陳倩揚同司勳都炒咗喇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69c991511b99f4618b7966f0c639b5f11895b1e1","tid":2442710,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T21:41:52.000Z","msg":"陳逸寧已經無做？唔怪得唔見咗咁耐"},{"pid":"18fa0b034bfd36353b9e38e3da704e7501f82688","tid":2442710,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T21:45:11.000Z","msg":"呢個節目d主持好似間中就會變"},{"pid":"e73be1cb20850a60e62204af251015e0ab042f33","tid":2442710,"uid":30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T05:13:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1311893665518086/posts/5427637023943709/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1311893665518086%2Fposts%2F5427637023943709%2F&d=XsjoyflP4JPXBkuZaWCkHZgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=80e49751\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.